  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550060/extras/67cc38091e6c014f8a57bea91b2a93cd.webp?t=1762064486\" width=206 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minesweeper is back, but this time it's together! Minesweeper Together is a logical puzzle board game about revealing cells and avoiding mines in a multiplayer environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550060/extras/e079709ea59eaa2854819268793bce48.webp?t=1762064486\" width=330 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you reveal cells, you will find numbers that indicate how many mines are surrounding those numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 5 different preset difficulties:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insane</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diabolical</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The selected difficulty dictates board width, board height, and mine count. You may also choose a custom difficulty to modify these values yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 total players online</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tutorial for those new or looking for a refresher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 11 \"glaggles\" to play as, or select the random option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A (almost) working no guessing mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw mode which allows you and others to doodle on the board to plan moves or just to have fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fresh take on the Minesweeper UI, with 39 selectable gameplay backgrounds with an included random option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 board themes to choose from with an included dark mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Workshop support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you're in a game, its up to you and your friends what to do on the board. Plan, draw, solve, or speedrun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come play Minesweeper, Together!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550060/extras/67cc38091e6c014f8a57bea91b2a93cd.webp?t=1762064486\" width=206 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minesweeper is back, but this time it's together! Minesweeper Together is a logical puzzle board game about revealing cells and avoiding mines in a multiplayer environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550060/extras/e079709ea59eaa2854819268793bce48.webp?t=1762064486\" width=330 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you reveal cells, you will find numbers that indicate how many mines are surrounding those numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 5 different preset difficulties:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insane</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diabolical</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The selected difficulty dictates board width, board height, and mine count. You may also choose a custom difficulty to modify these values yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 total players online</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tutorial for those new or looking for a refresher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 11 \"glaggles\" to play as, or select the random option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A (almost) working no guessing mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw mode which allows you and others to doodle on the board to plan moves or just to have fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fresh take on the Minesweeper UI, with 39 selectable gameplay backgrounds with an included random option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 board themes to choose from with an included dark mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Workshop support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you're in a game, its up to you and your friends what to do on the board. Plan, draw, solve, or speedrun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come play Minesweeper, Together!</p>",
